The paper deals with privacy and security issues on the web, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The analysis involves a large dataset and quantitative methods, which suggests the category of cybernetics (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the use of cookies and Javascript, which are related to programming languages and software engineering (cs.PR). Finally, the paper involves data analysis and statistics, which suggests the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
